                  <persName corresp="PRS0000" instant="false" full="yes">The names of the donors are mentioned in the supplication formulas throughout the Ms.: Wäldä Tǝnśaʾe (e.g., fols. 3ra, 6vb, 9vb, 10ra, 11ra, 12rb, 19ra), his wife Lahǝyä Dǝngǝl (e.g., fols. 6vb, 9vb, 10ra, 19ra, 22vb), his brother ʿƎquba Libanos (e.g., fols. 12rb, 14va, 19ra, 22vb) and his children Wäldä Yoḥannǝs (e.g., fols. 11ra, 16rb, 21va), Wäldä Maryam (e.g., fols. 11ra, 16rb, 21va), Gäbrä Ḥǝywät Solomon (e.g., fols. 15va, 21va), Wälättä Ḥǝywät (e.g., fols. 15va, 25ra), and Gäbrä Giyorgis (e.g., fols. 9vb, 10ra). &#xD;
Also, they are mentioned on fol. 48rb (s. Additio 1). &#xD;
